== 审判 ==
2006年11月25日，石悦军被以故意杀人罪判处[[死刑|死刑]]，<ref>[http://news.scotsman.com/topstories/Death-penalty-for-knife-killer.2830416.jp Death penalty for knife killer], ''[[The_Scotsman|The Scotsman]]'' (27 November 2006)</ref><ref>[http://www.chinadaily.com.cn/china/2006-11/25/content_742844.htm Killer sentenced to death in NE China] {{Wayback|url=http://www.chinadaily.com.cn/china/2006-11/25/content_742844.htm |date=20160811070403 }} [[中国日报|中国日报]] (25 November 2006)</ref><ref>[http://www.taipeitimes.com/News/world/archives/2006/11/27/2003338128 Court sentences butcher] {{Wayback|url=http://www.taipeitimes.com/News/world/archives/2006/11/27/2003338128 |date=20160701044636 }}, [[台北時報|台北時報]] (27 November 2006)</ref>同年12月20日在[[通化市|通化]]被枪决。<ref name="PD2112">[http://english.peopledaily.com.cn/200612/21/eng20061221_334523.html Butcher who slew 12 in NE China executed], [[人民日报|人民日报]] (21 December 2006)</ref> 

